text: Fig. 2. Membrane array analysis of DCA treated OE33 cells, 24 post-exposure. (a) Cancer pathway arrays were used to study gene expression abnormalities induced by 300 DCA relative to untreated OE33 cells. These example arrays show the up-regulation of the I and IL-8 genes by DCA. (b) Two example signal transduction arrays are shown; those hybridized with cDNA from untreated OE33 cells and cDNA from OE33 cells 24 after DCA exposure.
